### Enable Authentication

Go to **Authentication**:
```
https://xxxxx.supabase.co/project/default/auth/providers
```

Default enabled providers:
- Email/Password ✓
- (Optional) GitHub OAuth
- (Optional) Google OAuth

For MVP, Email/Password is sufficient.

